headline: J.P. Morgan Wealth Management Ranks #1 in J.D. Power Digital Experience Study
summary: NEW YORK, December 19, 2024--J.P. Morgan Wealth Management ranks best in customer satisfaction for both self-directed and full-service investors in the J.D. Power 2024 U.S. Wealth Management Digital Experience Study. This prestigious recognition measures customers’ satisfaction with wealth management websites and mobile apps.
